<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
Section 113(d)(3) of the Clean Air Act (42 U.S.C. 7413(d)) authorizes EPA to implement a field citation program. The
regulations in this part establish the standards and procedures which will apply to all field citations issued by
EPA under this authority. The field citation program is designed both to deter minor violations of the Act and to expedite
enforcement against such violations. 
