<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
to balance supply with demand at levels assuring stable supplies 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
for domestic and export use at prices that are considered 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
sufficient for producers. The national quota is based on 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
