Abstract: This action is needed to implement the national peanut poundage 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
quota, as required by statute. The purpose of the quota is to 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
balance supply with demand at a level that will assure stable 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
supplies for domestic use and assure producers a stable income. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
The export-edible sales price for additional peanuts provides 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
price stability for additional peanuts sold under contract and 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
assures handlers that CCC will not undercut export efforts. The 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
